1.	For verifying the cost and period of the project, we have relied on the work order issued by Ahmedabad Municipal Corporation to the concerned contractor for the purpose of construction of the housing scheme and the period mentioned in the work order.

2.	For the purpose of verifying the number of units in the project, we have relied on the Commencement letter issued by Ahmedabad Municipal Corporation.

3.	The figures placed in the owned funds, customer receipts and others (if any) in the sheet of Means of Finance have been relied on the information provided by the Ahmedabad Municipal Corporation vide its mail dated 25-11-2024.

4.	For the purpose of verifying the unit cost of the project, we have relied on circular no. AHM/102015/453/TH-1 dated 15-12-2016 issued by Urban Development & Urban Housing Department of Government of Gujarat.

5.	For the purpose of incurred & paid expense as mentioned in MOF of the project, we have considered the value of work completed as mentioned in the latest audited running account bill of the project.

formThreeIdData.notesToCertificate:
1. The amount of construction cost has been considered on the basis of the information provided by the competent authorities of the Corporation.
2. Total number of units to be constructed has been assumed to be built up evenly.
3. Land valuation method has been selected as "ASR value" based on the information provided by Housing Project Department vide it's mail dated 13-06-2024 which clarifies that "Jantri rates" have been adopted for land valuation.
4. As per Housing Cell department's mail dated 04-06-2024, we had been informed that draw has not yet been conducted for EWS-81.
5. We have considered GST as a part of expense incurred and paid till date in Form-3 based on the audited running account bill of the project.
6. All the expenses are covered under the scope of contractor and Ahmedabad Municipal Corporation makes the payment to the contractor based on the execution of work and as per tender's conditions. Hence, there are no separate on-site expenses considering which the amount is "0".
7. This Form-3 for registration is being filed as a response to the queries of RERA.
